node.text:
NEW PRODUCT ALERT! ⛔️

We are so pumped to bring to you The Lucky Quatro™ 110mm wheel! These wheels feature high quality Lucky urethane. Which are produced using our proven Lucky urethane formula with Lucky Rebound Technology™ (LRT™)
We have spent countless hours tweaking and adjusting our urethane formula and processes to improve the feel, performance, and durability of our wheels. Lucky Rebound Technology™ (LRT™) is a combination of high-performance urethane, a new pouring process, and a proprietary curing method which gives these wheels a grippy, fast, and buttery roll. 
Weight (per wheel) - .5lbs (0.22kg). Be on the look out for these wheels that will be dropping soon! #Scootering #NewProduct #Scooter #LuckyScooters 🍀
